      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>https://dasarpai.com/wiaposts/meaning-of-prakriti-in-bhagavad-gita/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://dasarpai.com/assets/images/wiapost/5293-meaning-of-prakriti-in-bhagavad-gita.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Meaning of Prakriti in Bhagwat Gita&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Meaning of Prakriti in Bhagwat Gita 
    &lt;div id=&#34;the-meaning-of-prakriti-in-bhagwat-gita&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
